{
  "id": "69fd1673ad6657c1ba74296c",
  "title": "左大腿骨骨幹部骨折、入院して手術します―2026/05/07",
  "created": 1778194036,
  "updated": 1778195027,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69fd1673ad6657c1ba74296c",
      "text": "左大腿骨骨幹部骨折、入院して手術します―2026/05/07",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194053
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16850000000000c7a62e",
      "text": "背景： [左大腿骨骨幹部骨折、入院して手術します]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194053,
      "updated": 1778194061
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16800000000000c7a62c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194048,
      "updated": 1778194048
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a612",
      "text": "from [2026/05/07]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194048
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16800000000000c7a62d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194048,
      "updated": 1778194048
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a614",
      "text": "[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194048
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a615",
      "text": " 昨日あさごはん食べたあと、胃痛と胸焼けがひどくて寝込んでた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a616",
      "text": "  ひるごはんとよるごはんをほとんど食べなかった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a617",
      "text": "  休める時はしっかり寝るんだぞー！[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a618",
      "text": "  食えるようになったらしっかり食うんだぞー！[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a619",
      "text": " 今日ようやく痛みが退いたので、大学etc.への連絡をやる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a61a",
      "text": " あさごはん食べた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a61b",
      "text": "  おなか痛くならない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a61c",
      "text": "  炎症？は収まったようだ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a61d",
      "text": "  順調に回復しているようで[いい話だ.icon][Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a61e",
      "text": " ひるごはん食べた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a61f",
      "text": " 　問題なし",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a620",
      "text": " 連絡まわりでlaptop使っていたら疲れちゃった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a621",
      "text": " リハビリした",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a622",
      "text": " 　[車椅子]に乗れた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194748
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a623",
      "text": " 　[点滴]しているので、[介助]が必要",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194745
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a624",
      "text": " 間接の可動域を確認した",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a625",
      "text": " 　少しずつ動かせる範囲を確認していく",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a626",
      "text": "　　寝返りを打てるようになった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a627",
      "text": "　　ベッドのそばの棚にも手が届くようになった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a628",
      "text": "　　応援[terang.icon][atohs.icon][bsahd.icon][Hiro Aki.icon][vlzs.icon][基素.icon][hoagecko.icon][Summer498.icon][mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778195027
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a629",
      "text": "　　赤ちゃんの成長記録くらいの一歩感。ことの重大さが伺える。ますます応援する。[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd16740000000000c7a62a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778194036,
      "updated": 1778194036
    }
  ]
}